      "id": "source",
      "durationMs": 31000,
      "narration": {
        "text": "The public API lives in com.codename1.ads. AdManager is the entry point, and there is a type per format: InterstitialAd, RewardedAd, RewardedInterstitialAd, AppOpenAd, BannerAd, and NativeAdLoader. Consent is handled by AdConsent (UMP plus iOS ATT), and AdConfig, AdRequest, and AdListener round out the surface."
      },
