      "id": "tradeoffs",
      "durationMs": 32500,
      "narration": {
        "text": "The reference provider is a real, modern AdMob integration shipped as maven/cn1-admob, modeled on the ML Kit cn1libs. It targets Google Mobile Ads v24 and up on Android, the current GAD APIs with UMP and ATT on iOS, and AdMob mediation works transparently behind it."
